metadata.name: Mythic Angel
metadata.description:
They say Platonic Love is the purest form of love. The idolization of our object of desire takes mythical propositions in our imagination and evokes strong feelings. 

Taking inspiration from the most romantic of art movements, the 
Pre-Raphaelite Brotherhood and using my signature stained glass collage technique, i tried to visualize the fragility of the new born love.
